  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db4\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dc3 \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd3\u0da5 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Petition from lawyer Priyalal that Sanath insulted the court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Lawyer Priyalal Sirisena has filed a petition in the Supreme Court today (29) requesting that a hearing be held and appropriate steps be taken regarding the statement that MP Sanath Nishantha insulted the court during a news conference held at the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna party headquarters.",
        "The respondents in this petition are the Member of Parliament Sanath Nishantha, the Sri Lanka Bar Association and the Governor.",
        "The first respondent of this petition is a suspect in the case pending in the Fort Magistrate's Court regarding the attack on the Galle Mudoora protest site on May 9th, and the petitioner has also stated in his petition that he has been accused of criminal incidents before.",
        "In his petition, the first respondent MP, who participated in a press conference held at the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna party office on the 23rd, made statements in a way that insulted the court and the entire judicial system was insulted by this."
      ],
